todos.title: API: faulty transcation handlings
todos.description: The internet, heard of it? Transfers half a petabyte of data a minute, do you have any idea how that happens? All of those YouPorn ones and zeros streaming directly to your crappy little smart phone day after day. Every douchebag who craps his pants if he can't get the new dubstep Skrillex remix in under 12 seconds. It's not magic, it's talent and sweat. So what do I do? I make sure that one bad config on one key component doesn't bankrupt the entire goddamn company. That's what I do.
